```
# Generated by Android Studio
*.iml
*.ipr
*.iws
.idea/

# Build and intermediate files
/build/
.gradle/
*/build/
*/intermediates/
*/outputs/
*.apk
*.aar

# Local configuration file (sdk path, etc)
local.properties

# Log Files
*.log

# Android Studio caches
.cache/

# Code coverage reports
coverage/
*.ec

# Proguard folder generated by Android Studio
/proguard/

# External native build folder generated in Android Studio
.externalNativeBuild/

# NDK
obj/
.libs/

# Environment variable files
.env
.env.local
*.env.*

# Python related (if any Python tools are used)
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd
.Python
*.so
.coverage
htmlcov/
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/

# Node.js related (if any web components)
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*

# General temp files
*.tmp
*.temp
*~
.swp
.swo

# OS generated files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
```